content:
You can create a calculation matrix that's part of a group of matrices. This speeds up Vlocity processing and frees up SOQL queries for other purposes.

Versions in a grouped matrix can have different effective dates.

To create a grouped calculation matrix, make sure your groups of matrices follow these rules:

* Identical input and output column headers
* Contain at least one and maximum two common input dimensions
* Input variable ranges must all be the same
* The Group Key and Sub Group Key cannot be range inputs

Create a Grouped Calculation Matrix. Populate the rest of the matrices in the group.

After you've created the first matrix, you can create as many other group members as you need.

Versions in a grouped matrix can have different effective dates.
title: Creating a Grouped Calculation Matrix
